          lQhbnd[(z*{{nDof3D}}+x)*{{nDataPad}}+n+{{3*nDof*nDof3D*nDataPad}}] += lQhi[((z*{{nDof3D}}+y)*{{nDof}}+x)*{{nDataPad}}+n] * FRCoeff[y];
